{"tid":2345861,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"徵求爆料 建立英國黃色經濟圈","createTime":"2020-12-30T01:05:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T00:42:53.000Z","uid":1799,"like":68,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"9ad45d11f16a9a9756f774b63662ca37330c8ce5","tid":2345861,"uid":1799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T01:05:25.000Z","msg":"英國黃藍經濟圈爆料Google Form：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdihaSUVmCQF8vYpFcC7IfJ2q2uUF6Wlgdok3zAQCY5-rSb4A/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdihaSUVmCQF8vYpFcC7IfJ2q2uUF6Wlgdok3zAQCY5-rSb4A%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=adcaba23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdihaSUVmCQF8vYpFcC7IfJ2q2uUF6Wlgdok3zAQCY5-rSb4A/viewform?usp=sf_link</a><br />\n(updated version, 唔洗留個人資料)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曼市華埠街坊商會前會長陳新貴於Facebook無的放矢，抹黑於12月12號嘅合法和平集會，此舉動嚴重干涉了英國內政，是赤裸裸的霸權行徑，暖氣軍師撐香港堅決反對。中大理大守衛戰一周年悼念集會，事先有依法向警方申請，當時有英國警方在場觀察。中方制裁澳洲導致中國人民缺煤停電，陳新貴不顧祖國同胞飽受霜寒之苦，反而關心在英港人嘅集會權益，無不暴露著紅色勢力插手英國內政的卑劣行徑，更意圖組織群眾「去對應呢班人」，其背後讓紅色勢力滲透英國的政治圖謀早已是&ldquo;司馬昭之心&rdquo;，每一個人都應看清這樣的險惡用心！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HdSWske.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHdSWske.png&h=d5aa2aaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳新貴講嘅係廣東話，於1966年前倚仗英國政府施恩得以移民英國，係祖國同胞受文化大革命煎熬嘅同時，自己則享受民主自由帶黎嘅經濟繁榮。如今竟打壓港人合法權益、干涉英國內政，如此背宗忘祖嘅行為，必會牢牢地釘在歷史的恥辱柱上！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MF6TuyD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMF6TuyD.png&h=11ccbf1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳新貴於接受D100訪問時堅稱抹黑抗爭者為「亂港廢青」係冇問題，其一錯再錯，死不悔改嘅態度已引致眾叛親離，包括英國創城地產嘅割席，此舉只係拿石頭砸自己的腳，燃點每一個人於英國推行黃色經濟圈嘅意志。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qnPmDtY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqnPmDtY.png&h=7c1a64c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 曼市華埠街坊商會於12月18號稱陳新貴已辭任會長，但到12月23號仲用緊陳新貴嘅email，其惺惺作态令人感到嘔心。目前，對抗暴政、光復香港乃大勢所趨、民心所向，陳新貴及曼市華埠街坊商會del左post就裝聾作啞，意欲何為？是擔心藏不住自己做的腌臢事，還是怕惹怒未來數十萬計以BNO5+1計劃移民英國嘅香港人，從此丟了「賣港賺錢」的路子？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3d2vwPS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3d2vwPS.jpg&h=1fa87ee6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n參與討論 / Forum<br />\nTG公海：<a href=\"https://t.me/justitiahongkong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjustitiahongkong&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=781b4544\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/justitiahongkong</a><br />\nTG Channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/BoilerTacticians\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FBoilerTacticians&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=c19afaf9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/BoilerTacticians</a><br />\nIG: <a href=\"https://instagram.com/justitiahk?igshid=9eheab7n4pkw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fjustitiahk%3Figshid%3D9eheab7n4pkw&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=4b362949\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/justitiahk?igshid=9eheab7n4pkw</a><br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/JustitiaHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FJustitiaHK%2F&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=89d895fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/JustitiaHK/</a><br />\n課金支持 / Support Us<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/hmbnxs-justice-for-hong-kong?fbclid=IwAR3qibQNkZ06RutUJ4vRmrI1by5stzhWLkAbKoDyPhYMXi6ebKcGJ1G6YvY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fhmbnxs-justice-for-hong-kong%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3qibQNkZ06RutUJ4vRmrI1by5stzhWLkAbKoDyPhYMXi6ebKcGJ1G6YvY&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=c3ed5a21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gofundme.com/f/hmbnxs-justice-for-hong-kong?fbclid=IwAR3qibQNkZ06RutUJ4vRmrI1by